---
title: Glazed Halloumi, Orange & Radish Salad with Avocado, Parmesan & Balsamic Dressing
description: A refreshing salad is exactly what we want when the warm weather hits. This one brings together an epic combo of flavours, with
sweet-and-salty glazed halloumi, citrusy orange segments, creamy avo and nutty almonds. It has a little bit of everything you
need and it’s sure to go down a treat!
